<br>
Which is why, nowadays, i not only dont want to use a pet there myself, but for my safety and the safety of the raid, i dont want anyone else using pets except for certain situations...its honestly just not worth it with a raid force there anyway.<br>
<br>
Sometimes ill pull out a pet if we get three spitegolems or something crazy like that. but most of the time i get jittery when i see pets there.<br>
<br>
